editorial.title: Wayne
content: Days Inn by Wyndham Wayne is located in Wayne. Rhino Theatre and Shea Center for the Performing Arts are cultural highlights, and travelers looking to shop may want to visit Willowbrook Mall and Westfield Garden State Plaza. Jumpnasium Kids Parties & More and Monster Mini Golf are also worth visiting.

content.text: When visiting Wayne, Days Inn by Wyndham Wayne is a great choice to consider. Guests can visit the health club for a workout, and free perks include WiFi, self parking, and on-the-go breakfast daily between 6:30 AM and 9:30 AM. Fellow travelers like the helpful staff and location.

content.text: • Rollaway beds are available for USD 10.0 per night

This property advises that enhanced cleaning and guest safety measures are currently in place.

Disinfectant is used to clean the property, and commonly-touched surfaces are cleaned with disinfectant between stays.

Social distancing measures are in place; staff at the property wear personal protective equipment; a shield is in place between staff and guests in main contact areas; guests are provided with hand sanitizer; masks are required in public areas for unvaccinated guests.

Contactless check-out is available.

This property affirms that it follows the cleaning and disinfection practices of Count on Us (Wyndham).
